s", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:34:47Z"}}, "4": {"text": "That joke landed because it felt true. Clothing terminology can sound needlessly compl\u2026 [+6068 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.realmenrealstyle.com/pants-trousers-menswear/", "title": "Men\u2019s Pants Terms Explained: Trousers vs Slacks vs Chinos vs Khakis", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:34:47Z"}}, "5": {"text": "UK Strengthens Trade Partnership with Uganda. The Westminster Africa Business Association and South Asian Chamber of Commerce and Industry was in Kampala to explore opportunities. Ugandan businesses and workers stand tobenefitfrom new partnerships as a major UK business delegation arrives in Kampala this week.Invited by the Rt.\u00a0Honourable Prime Minister Robinah Nabbanja, durin\u2026 [+5435 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.gov.uk/government/news/uk-strengthens-trade-partnership-with-uganda", "title": "UK Strengthens Trade Partnership with Uganda", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:32:00Z"}}, "6": {"text": "Outgoing BBC Director General to lead Creative Industries Council. Tim Davie to succeed current industry co-chair Sir Peter Bazalgette from 1 August <ul><li>He will co-chair with Baroness Shriti Vadera until she steps down on 31 December at the end of her term</li><li>Davie will advocate for the creative industries and work with the government to\u2026 [+3886 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.gov.uk/government/news/outgoing-bbc-director-general-to-lead-creative-industries-council", "title": "Outgoing BBC Director General to lead Creative Industries Council", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:31:29Z"}}, "7": {"text": "Titans make trip to Texas Tech\u2019s pro day four weeks before NFL Draft. The Titans attended Texas Tech\u2019s Pro Day on Thursday as Tennessee, as well as the Red Raiders\u2019 top prospects, gear up for the 2026 NFL Draft. Texas Techs Pro Day was one that the Tennessee Titans did not intend to miss.", "metadata": {"source": "https://titanswire.usatoday.com/story/sports/nfl/titans/2026/03/27/tennessee-titans-texas-tech-pro-day-nfl-draft/89340166007/", "title": "Titans make trip to Texas Tech\u2019s pro day four weeks before NFL Draft", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:31:05Z"}}, "8": {"text": "Texas Tech held its annual event on Thursday, the same day as eight other programs around the country, including Florida\u2026 [+1262 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://titanswire.usatoday.com/story/sports/nfl/titans/2026/03/27/tennessee-titans-texas-tech-pro-day-nfl-draft/89340166007/", "title": "Titans make trip to Texas Tech\u2019s pro day four weeks before NFL Draft", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:31:05Z"}}, "9": {"text": "Jameson owner Pernod Ricard in merger talks to US group behind Jack Daniels. Discussions take place against a challenging backdrop for global drinks industry amid subdued demand and tariffs Shares in Pernod Ricard, the French drinks giant behind Jameson and Powers Irish whiskey, rose on Friday after the group confirmed it is in merger discussions with Jack Daniels whiskey owner, Brown F\u2026 [+2198", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.irishtimes.com/business/2026/03/27/jameson-owner-pernod-ricard-in-merger-talks-to-us-group-behind-jack-daniels/", "title": "Jameson owner Pernod Ricard in merger talks to US group behind Jack Daniels", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:22Z"}}, "10": {"text": "with Jack Daniels whiskey owner, Brown F\u2026 [+2198 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.irishtimes.com/business/2026/03/27/jameson-owner-pernod-ricard-in-merger-talks-to-us-group-behind-jack-daniels/", "title": "Jameson owner Pernod Ricard in merger talks to US group behind Jack Daniels", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:22Z"}}, "11": {"text": "Auguries of Failure: Israel Invades Lebanon, Yet Again. When will Israel realise that invading Lebanon with paralytic compulsion can never be the solution to its security ills?", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globalresearch.ca/israel-invades-lebanon-yet-again/5920305", "title": "Auguries of Failure: Israel Invades Lebanon, Yet Again", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:17Z"}}, "12": {"text": "Having destroyed Gaza with existential, illegal fury, the Israeli Defense Forces have commenced operations in Lebanon with a similar, dev\u2026 When will Israel realise that invading Lebanon with paralytic compulsion can never be the solution to its security ills? \r\nHaving destroyed Gaza with existential, illegal fury, the Israeli Defense Fo\u2026 [+6534 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globalresearch.ca/israel-invades-lebanon-yet-again/5920305", "title": "Auguries of Failure: Israel Invades Lebanon, Yet Again", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:17Z"}}, "13": {"text": "The RAM crisis is here \u2014 and it may ruin these 5 Android phones. From Google to Samsung and beyond, here are five Android phones that could be ruined by the ongoing RAM crisis. RAM prices have exploded in recent months owing to demand from AI-related companies. Unfortunately, this has resulted in various tech products seeing price increases, too.\r\nSmartphones arent immune t\u2026 [+5946 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.androidauthority.com/android-phones-ruined-ram-crisis-3649724/", "title": "The RAM crisis is here \u2014 and it may ruin these 5 Android phones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:10Z"}}, "14": {"text": "Official Statistics: UK trade in goods by business characteristics 2024. UK overseas trade in goods statistics (OTS) data has been linked with the Office for National Statistics (ONS) business statistics. HM Revenue &amp; Customs (HMRC) has linked the UK overseas trade in goods statistics (OTS) with business statistics from the Office for National Statistics (ONS) Inter-Departmental Business", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/uk-trade-in-goods-by-business-characteristics-2024", "title": "Official Statistics: UK trade in goods by business characteristics 2024", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:02Z"}}, "15": {"text": "Statistics (ONS) Inter-Departmental Business Register \u2026 [+381 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/uk-trade-in-goods-by-business-characteristics-2024", "title": "Official Statistics: UK trade in goods by business characteristics 2024", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:02Z"}}, "16": {"text": "UK trade in goods by business characteristics 2024: data tables. Supporting tables for the UK trade in goods by business characteristics 2024 We use some essential cookies to make this website work.\r\nWed like to set additional cookies to understand how you use GOV.UK, remember your settings and improve government services.\r\nWe also use coo\u2026 [+70 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.gov.uk/government/statistical-data-sets/uk-trade-in-goods-by-business-characteristics-2024-data-tables", "title": "UK trade in goods by business characteristics 2024: data tables", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:02Z"}}, "17": {"text": "A full-time engineer with multiple side hustles found the most passive one: ATMs and vending machines earn him $1,500 a month for a few hours of work. William Butterton doesn't believe in passive income, but he thinks he's found the closest thing: ATMs. William Butterton is a full-time engineer who does ATM and vending placement on the side.Chona Kasinger for BI", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.businessinsider.com/passive-income-side-hustles-atm-vending-machines-small-business-2026-3", "title": "A full-time engineer with multiple side hustles found the most passive one: ATMs and vending machines earn him $1,500 a month for a few hours of work", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:01Z"}}, "18": {"text": "<ul><li>William Butterton is a full-time engineer who has experimented with a variety o\u2026 [+6254 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.businessinsider.com/passive-income-side-hustles-atm-vending-machines-small-business-2026-3", "title": "A full-time engineer with multiple side hustles found the most passive one: ATMs and vending machines earn him $1,500 a month for a few hours of work", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:01Z"}}, "19": {"text": "Pruritus Therapeutics Market Size is Projected to Reach USD 15.58 Billion by 2035 Due to the Increasing Cases of Chronic Inflammatory Skin Diseases Globally | SNS Insider. Pruritus therapeutics market to reach $15.58 Bn by 2035, driven by rising skin disorders, strong biologics pipeline, and expanding global treatment demand. Austin, March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- According to SNS Insider,", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263619/0/en/Pruritus-Therapeutics-Market-Size-is-Projected-to-Reach-USD-15-58-Billion-by-2035-Due-to-the-Increasing-Cases-of-Chronic-Inflammatory-Skin-Diseases-Globally-SNS-Insider.html", "title": "Pruritus Therapeutics Market Size is Projected to Reach USD 15.58 Billion by 2035 Due to the Increasing Cases of Chronic Inflammatory Skin Diseases Globally | SNS Insider", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:00Z"}}, "20": {"text": "(GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- According to SNS Insider, the\u00a0Pruritus Therapeutics Market\u00a0size was valued at USD 10.30 billion in 2025 and is expected to reach USD 15.58 billion by 2035, \u2026 [+8984 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263619/0/en/Pruritus-Therapeutics-Market-Size-is-Projected-to-Reach-USD-15-58-Billion-by-2035-Due-to-the-Increasing-Cases-of-Chronic-Inflammatory-Skin-Diseases-Globally-SNS-Insider.html", "title": "Pruritus Therapeutics Market Size is Projected to Reach USD 15.58 Billion by 2035 Due to the Increasing Cases of Chronic Inflammatory Skin Diseases Globally | SNS Insider", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:00Z"}}, "21": {"text": "Trump Extends the Extension on Iran in Preparation for \u201cFalse Flag\u201d?. The Midterms are around the corner if we make it that long\u2026 So far, every Trump backed candidate is trailin