d up 10.5% during mid-day trading on Wednesday . The stock traded as high as C$0.84 and last traded at C$0.84. 145,937 shares were traded during mid-day trading, a decline of 34% from the average session volume of 222,566 shares. The stock had previously closed at [...]", "metadata": {"source": "https://baseballnewssource.com/2026/03/27/neptune-digital-assets-cvenda-trading-up-10-5-heres-why/11074874.html", "title": "Neptune Digital Assets (CVE:NDA) Trading Up 10.5% \u2013 Here\u2019s Why", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:16:41"}}, "235": {"text": "shares. The stock had previously closed at [...] ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://baseballnewssource.com/2026/03/27/neptune-digital-assets-cvenda-trading-up-10-5-heres-why/11074874.html", "title": "Neptune Digital Assets (CVE:NDA) Trading Up 10.5% \u2013 Here\u2019s Why", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:16:41"}}, "236": {"text": "Paramount plans to invest $30 billion in content after acquiring Warner Bros. Miami.- Paramount Skydance President and CEO David Ellison predicted this Friday a 30 billion dollar investment in content, above competitors like Netflix and Disney, after the acquisition of Warner Brothers. Ellison asserted at a conference in Miami that \"the combined company\", based on 2026 figures, represents a", "metadata": {"source": "https://deultimominuto.net/en/uncategorized/paramount-plans-to-invest-30-billion-in-content-after-acquiring-warner-bros/", "title": "Paramount plans to invest $30 billion in content after acquiring Warner Bros", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:16:35"}}, "237": {"text": "company\", based on 2026 figures, represents a business that generates $69 billion in revenue, $18 [...] La entrada Paramount plans to invest $30 billion in content after acquiring Warner Bros se publico\u0301 primero en De U\u0301ltimo Minuto English . ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://deultimominuto.net/en/uncategorized/paramount-plans-to-invest-30-billion-in-content-after-acquiring-warner-bros/", "title": "Paramount plans to invest $30 billion in content after acquiring Warner Bros", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:16:35"}}, "238": {"text": "Top MBA / PGDM Colleges in Jammu & Kashmir: Fees, Rankings, Admissions. There are 22 colleges for MBA / PGDM in Jammu & Kashmir. These colleges have various programs like MBA, MBA Health Care & Hospital Management, MBA in Craft Management and Entrepreneurship, MBA in Agri Business Management with fees ranging from \u20b960,000 ... ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.collegesearch.in/mba/colleges-jammu-kashmir", "title": "Top MBA / PGDM Colleges in Jammu & Kashmir: Fees, Rankings, Admissions", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:16:26"}}, "239": {"text": "State-Level Viksit Bharat Youth Parliament held. The State-Level Viksit Bharat Youth Parliament 2026 was held on Friday at Japfu Christian College, Kigwema, bringing together young participants from across Nagaland for democratic deliberations and parliamentary practice.The topic discussed in Youth Parliament 2026 was \u201cUnion Budget 2026 \u2013 Strengthening the Indian Youth Path Towards Viksit Bharat", "metadata": {"source": "https://nagalandpost.com/state-level-viksit-bharat-youth-parliament-held/", "title": "State-Level Viksit Bharat Youth Parliament held", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:16:24"}}, "240": {"text": "the Indian Youth Path Towards Viksit Bharat 2047.\u201dDelivering the keynote address, Dr. Salam Dhanachandra [...] The post State-Level Viksit Bharat Youth Parliament held first appeared on Nagaland Post . ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://nagalandpost.com/state-level-viksit-bharat-youth-parliament-held/", "title": "State-Level Viksit Bharat Youth Parliament held", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:16:24"}}, "241": {"text": "Spotlight on the News: WSU Profs. Khan & Lupovitch on inside the Iran War. On Sunday, March 29, Spotlight on the News will take viewers inside the intricacies, history, and politics of the Iran War. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.wxyz.com/news/political/spotlight-on-the-news/spotlight-on-the-news-wsu-profs-khan-lupovitch-on-inside-the-iran-war", "title": "Spotlight on the News: WSU Profs. Khan & Lupovitch on inside the Iran War", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:16:03"}}, "242": {"text": "ZEN Petroleum to list on GSE after securing fully subscribed IPO. ZEN Petroleum Holdings PLC has unveiled plans to raise GH\u00a2640 million through an initial public offering, marking one of the largest listings by an indigenous downstream petroleum company on the Ghana Stock Exchange in recent years. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.myjoyonline.com/zen-petroleum-to-list-on-gse-after-securing-fully-subscribed-ipo/", "title": "ZEN Petroleum to list on GSE after securing fully subscribed IPO", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:33:00"}}, "243": {"text": "Moniepoint Enters Kenyan Market with Majority Stake in Sumac Microfinance Bank. Nigerian fintech unicorn Moniepoint has successfully entered the Kenyan market by acquiring a 78% majority stake in Sumac Microfinance Bank, marking its first major expansion into East Africa. The deal, which was approved by the Competition Authority of Kenya (CAK), comes after years of attempts by Moniepoint to", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.tekedia.com/moniepoint-enters-kenyan-market-with-majority-stake-in-sumac-microfinance-bank/", "title": "Moniepoint Enters Kenyan Market with Majority Stake in Sumac Microfinance Bank", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:32:56"}}, "244": {"text": "comes after years of attempts by Moniepoint to establish a presence in the East African [...] The post Moniepoint Enters Kenyan Market with Majority Stake in Sumac Microfinance Bank appeared first on Tekedia . ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.tekedia.com/moniepoint-enters-kenyan-market-with-majority-stake-in-sumac-microfinance-bank/", "title": "Moniepoint Enters Kenyan Market with Majority Stake in Sumac Microfinance Bank", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:32:56"}}, "245": {"text": "Marching against hunger. Marching against hunger TONY BRITT Fri, 03/27/2026 - 19:32 ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.lakecityreporter.com/local-newsletter/marching-against-hunger", "title": "Marching against hunger", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:32:50"}}, "246": {"text": "Should You Apply for an O-1 or EB-1A Visa?. Professionals with exceptional achievements often ask the same question when they begin exploring U.S. immigration options: should I apply for an O-1 or EB-1A v ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://natlawreview.com/article/should-you-apply-o-1-or-eb-1a-visa", "title": "Should You Apply for an O-1 or EB-1A Visa?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:32:21"}}, "247": {"text": "It was another week when it paid to get out of anything in tech that used to be good: Jim Cramer. 'Mad Money' host Jim Cramer looks back at this week's market action. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.cnbc.com/video/2026/03/27/it-was-another-week-when-it-paid-to-get-out-of-anything-in-tech-that-used-to-be-good-jim-cramer.html", "title": "It was another week when it paid to get out of anything in tech that used to be good: Jim Cramer", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:32:21"}}, "248": {"text": "Huawei\u2019s Ascend 950PR AI Chip Just Won Over Chinese Customers By Mimicking CUDA Through CANN Next, Threatening NVIDIA\u2019s Moat. Huawei's newest AI chip, the Ascend 950PR, might not deliver strong compute performance relative to NVIDIA for domestic hyperscalers, but it offers a major upgrade with CUDA compatibility. Huawei's Ascend 950PR Sees Massive Interest, Mainly With CUDA-Like Programming", "metadata": {"source": "https://wccftech.com/huawei-ascend-950pr-just-won-over-chinese-customers-by-mimicking-cuda/", "title": "Huawei\u2019s Ascend 950PR AI Chip Just Won Over Chinese Customers By Mimicking CUDA Through CANN Next, Threatening NVIDIA\u2019s Moat", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:32:07"}}, "249": {"text": "Interest, Mainly With CUDA-Like Programming Brought In With CANN Next The Chinese computing industry has been trying to challenge NVIDIA's market dominance, and while the focus has been on upgrading offerings in terms of architecture and onboard features, it hasn't worked out to a large extent. Reports suggest that Chinese hyperscalers remain strongly inclined toward NVIDIA's hardware, and a key", "metadata": {"source": "https://wccftech.com/huawei-ascend-950pr-just-won-over-chinese-customers-by-mimicking-cuda/", "title": "Huawei\u2019s Ascend 950PR AI Chip Just Won Over Chinese Customers By Mimicking CUDA Through CANN Next, Threatening NVIDIA\u2019s Moat", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:32:07"}}, "250": {"text": "inclined toward NVIDIA's hardware, and a key reason isn't just the compute gap; CUDA [...] ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://wccftech.com/huawei-ascend-950pr-just-won-over-chinese-customers-by-mimicking-cuda/", "title": "Huawei\u2019s Ascend 950PR AI Chip Just Won Over Chinese Customers By Mimicking CUDA Through CANN Next, Threatening NVIDIA\u2019s Moat", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:32:07"}}, "251": {"text": "Rising Demand for Hair Transplants Reflects Changing Attitudes Toward Confidence and Self-Care. Advancements in technology, social acceptance, and long-term results drive growing interest across the UK March 27, 2026 - United Kingdom - Hair transplantation is experiencing a significant surge in popularity across the United Kingdom, as more individuals turn to advanced medical ONLY AVAILABLE IN", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.openpr.com/news/4444212/rising-demand-for-hair-transplants-reflects-changing-attitudes", "title": "Rising Demand for Hair Transplants Reflects Changing Attitudes Toward Confidence and Self-Care", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:32:04