nsus Bureau data, the population growth in the United States is slowing, however, the Houston area's growth tops the growth estimate list.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:38:34"}}, "259": {"text": "Global Meningitis Deaths Top 250K in 2023, Kids Hit Hard. In 2023, globally 259,000 people died from meningitis and 2.5 million people were infected with the disease, suggests a study published in The Lancet ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.miragenews.com/global-meningitis-deaths-top-250k-in-2023-kids-1646245/", "title": "Global Meningitis Deaths Top 250K in 2023, Kids Hit Hard", "description": "In 2023, globally 259,000 people died from meningitis and 2.5 million people were infected with the disease, suggests a study published in The Lancet", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:38:18"}}, "260": {"text": "Purdue Basketball Know Your Enemy: Arizona Wildcats. I get the lowdown from an Arizona Wildcat Expert. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://sports.yahoo.com/articles/purdue-basketball-know-enemy-arizona-233805149.html", "title": "Purdue Basketball Know Your Enemy: Arizona Wildcats", "description": "I get the lowdown from an Arizona Wildcat Expert.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:38:05"}}, "261": {"text": "Govt sets up task force to study impact of social media on minors. The government resolution dated March 25, which notified the task force, said the recent Economic Survey published by the finance ministry has expressed serious concern regarding the impact of increasing social media use among minors on their mental and physical health ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.hindustantimes.com/cities/mumbai-news/govt-sets-up-task-force-to-study-impact-of-social-media-on-minors-101774637254369.html", "title": "Govt sets up task force to study impact of social media on minors", "description": "The government resolution dated March 25, which notified the task force, said the recent Economic Su