an Diego); and NBC Connecticut and Telemundo Connecticut. Follow on social @NBCUFoundation and #LocalImpactGrants. About Comcast Comcast Corporation (Nasdaq: CMCSA) is a global media and technology company. From the connectivity and platforms we provide, to the content and experiences we create, our businesses reach hundreds of millions of customers, viewers, and guests worldwide. We deliver world-class broadband, wireless, and video through Xfinity, Comcast Business, and Sky; produce, distribute, and stream leading entertainment, sports, and news through brands including NBC, Telemundo, Universal, Peacock, and Sky; and bring incredible theme parks and attractions to life through Universal Destinations & Experiences. Visit www.comcastcorporation.com for more information. Only for Cyprus section No", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:26:12"}}, "444": {"text": "Pubs fight to stay open until early hours despite objections. TWO Weymouth pubs will be fighting for changes to their hours \u2013 after objections. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.dorsetecho.co.uk/news/25973708.objections-lodged-two-weymouth-town-pubs-proposed-opening-hours/", "title": "Pubs fight to stay open until early hours despite objections", "description": "TWO Weymouth pubs will be fighting for changes to their hours \u2013 after objections.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:30:00"}}, "445": {"text": "Skill Connect 2026 Conclave Held at CM Shri School Delhi. The first Industry\u2013Academia Conclave under Skill Connect 2026 was organized in Delhi, focusing on skill development, internships and industry collaboration for students. 27 March 2026, Delhi. The Government of Delhi organized the first Industry\u2013Academia Conclave under \u201cSkill Connect 2026\u201d at CM Shri School, Civil Lines. Delhi Education", "metadata": {"source": "https://cliqindia.com/skill-connect-2026-conclave-held-at-cm-shri-school-delhi/275766/", "title": "Skill Connect 2026 Conclave Held at CM Shri School Delhi", "description": "The first Industry\u2013Academia Conclave under Skill Connect 2026 was organized in Delhi, focusing on skill development, internships and industry collaboration for students. 27 March 2026, Delhi. The Government of Delhi organized the first Industry\u2013Academia Conclave under \u201cSkill Connect 2026\u201d at CM Shri School, Civil Lines. Delhi Education Minister Ashish Sood attended the", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:30:00"}}, "446": {"text": "at CM Shri School, Civil Lines. Delhi Education Minister Ashish Sood attended the ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://cliqindia.com/skill-connect-2026-conclave-held-at-cm-shri-school-delhi/275766/", "title": "Skill Connect 2026 Conclave Held at CM Shri School Delhi", "description": "The first Industry\u2013Academia Conclave under Skill Connect 2026 was organized in Delhi, focusing on skill development, internships and industry collaboration for students. 27 March 2026, Delhi. The Government of Delhi organized the first Industry\u2013Academia Conclave under \u201cSkill Connect 2026\u201d at CM Shri School, Civil Lines. Delhi Education Minister Ashish Sood attended the", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:30:00"}}, "447": {"text": "College group named finalist in healthcare business awards. South Hampshire College Group has been named a finalist in the SEHTA Healthcare Business Awards. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.dailyecho.co.uk/news/25974000.south-hampshire-college-group-named-finalist-awards/", "title": "College group named finalist in healthcare business awards", "description": "South Hampshire College Group has been named a finalist in the SEHTA Healthcare Business Awards.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:30:00"}}, "448": {"text": "Law firm with offices in Southampton target of potential takeover. A law firm with offices in Southampton could become the target of a potential takeover. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.dailyecho.co.uk/news/25973376.moore-barlow-discussions-takeover-knights-group/", "title": "Law firm with offices in Southampton target of potential takeover", "description": "A law firm with offices in Southampton could become the target of a potential takeover.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:30:00"}}, "449": {"text": "New forensic technology launched to tackle Southampton retail crime. A new forensic technology has been launched to help police in Southampton tackle retail crime. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.dailyecho.co.uk/news/25965070.new-forensic-technology-launched-tackle-retail-crime/", "title": "New forensic technology launched to tackle Southampton retail crime", "description": "A new forensic technology has been launched to help police in Southampton tackle retail crime.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:30:00"}}, "450": {"text": "DHS funding bill passes House, but shutdown drags on as Senate approves its own plan. The House passed a measure to fund the Department of Homeland Security for 60 days \u2014 but it's still unclear how the shutdown will end as the Senate, which approved its own funding plan, is on recess. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.cbsnews.com/minnesota/live-updates/dhs-shutdown-2026-senate-funding-day-42/", "title": "DHS funding bill passes House, but shutdown drags on as Senate approves its own plan", "description": "The House passed a measure to fund the Department of Homeland Security for 60 days \u2014 but it's still unclear how the shutdown will end as the Senate, which approved its own funding plan, is on recess.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:30:00"}}, "451": {"text": "HKIC chief sees growing opportunities in cutting-edge tech across China and Hong Kong. Investment opportunities in cutting-edge technologies are increasingly concentrated in mainland China and Hong Kong, according to Clara Chan Ka-chai, CEO of the Hong Kong Investment Corporation (HKIC). As the Hong Kong government\u2019s investment arm, the HKIC aimed to play a stronger role in attracting capital into", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3348227/hkic-chief-sees-growing-opportunities-cutting-edge-tech-across-china-and-hong-kong", "title": "HKIC chief sees growing opportunities in cutting-edge tech across China and Hong Kong", "description": "Investment opportunities in cutting-edge technologies are increasingly concentrated in mainland China and Hong Kong, according to Clara Chan Ka-chai, CEO of the Hong Kong Investment Corporation (HKIC). As the Hong Kong government\u2019s investment arm, the HKIC aimed to play a stronger role in attracting capital into high-potential projects and scaling investments through broader funding participation, Chan said during a panel session at the Boao Forum for Asia on Friday. Founded in 2022, the HKIC...", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:29:52"}}, "452": {"text": "play a stronger role in attracting capital into high-potential projects and scaling investments through broader funding participation, Chan said during a panel session at the Boao Forum for Asia on Friday. Founded in 2022, the HKIC... ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3348227/hkic-chief-sees-growing-opportunities-cutting-edge-tech-across-china-and-hong-kong", "title": "HKIC chief sees growing opportunities in cutting-edge tech across China and Hong Kong", "description": "Investment opportunities in cutting-edge technologies are increasingly concentrated in mainland China and Hong Kong, according to Clara Chan Ka-chai, CEO of the Hong Kong Investment Corporation (HKIC). As the Hong Kong government\u2019s investment arm, the HKIC aimed to play a stronger role in attracting capital into high-potential projects and scaling investments through broader funding participation, Chan said during a panel session at the Boao Forum for Asia on Friday. Founded in 2022, the HKIC...", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:29:52"}}, "453": {"text": "World\u2019s happiest country offers free Lake District vacation \u2014 here's how to apply. After eight straight years atop the global happiness rankings, Finland is inviting travelers to a free nature getaway in Europe\u2019s largest lake region, complete with saunas, a rental car and cabin stays \u2014 here\u2019s how to win the trip ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.ynetnews.com/travel/article/bje0p6vs11x", "title": "World\u2019s happiest country offers free Lake District vacation \u2014 here's how to apply", "description": "After eight straight years atop the global happiness rankings, Finland is inviting travelers to a free nature getaway in Europe\u2019s largest lake region, complete with saunas, a rental car and cabin stays \u2014 here\u2019s how to win the trip", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:29:33"}}, "454": {"text": "US envoy hopeful on Iran talks as strikes target nuclear facilities. TEHRAN (AFP) : US President Donald Trump\u2019s special envoy Steve Witkoff said Friday (Mar 27) he believes Iran will hold talks with Washington \u201cthis week\u201d to end the month-long war, as US-Israeli strikes hit two Iranian nuclear facilities. Iran threatened retaliation against industrial sites in the region, with no clear end to the", "metadata": {"source": "https://thefrontierpost.com/us-envoy-hopeful-on-iran-talks-as-strikes-target-nuclear-facilities/", "title": "US envoy hopeful on Iran talks as strikes target nuclear facilities", "description": "TEHRAN (AFP) : US President Donald Trump\u2019s special envoy Steve Witkoff said Friday (Mar 27) he believes Iran will hold talks with Washington \u201cthis week\u201d to end the month-long war, as US-Israeli strikes hit two Iranian nuclear facilities. Iran threatened retaliation against industrial sites in the region, with no clear end to the conflict in [...]", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03