 cut excise duties to offset rising global crude costs. Petrol holds at INR 94.77 in Delhi and INR 103.54 in Mumbai. Despite international volatility and high prices in cities like Hyderabad, the move aims to shield consumers from inflation and stabilize domestic fuel rates.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:47:13"}}, "467": {"text": "prices in cities like Hyderabad, the move aims to shield consumers from inflation and stabilize domestic fuel rates. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.latestly.com/business/petrol-price-today-march-28-2026-check-petrol-rates-in-delhi-mumbai-chennai-and-other-cities-7370389.html", "title": "Petrol Price Today, March 28, 2026: Check Petrol Rates in Delhi, Mumbai, Chennai and Other Cities", "description": "Today, March 28, India's petrol prices (petrol rates) remained steady as the government cut excise duties to offset rising global crude costs. Petrol holds at INR 94.77 in Delhi and INR 103.54 in Mumbai. Despite international volatility and high prices in cities like Hyderabad, the move aims to shield consumers from inflation and stabilize domestic fuel rates.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:47:13"}}, "468": {"text": "IMF, Pakistan reach staff-level agreement on $1.2b disbursement. IMF staff reached an agreement with Pakistan, unlocking $1.2B under EFF and RSF, supporting economic recovery, macro stability, and social protection amid global risks. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://dunyanews.tv/en/Business/942820-imf-pakistan-reach-stafflevel-agreement-on-12b-disbursement", "title": "IMF, Pakistan reach staff-level agreement on $1.2b disbursement", "description": "IMF staff reached an agreement with Pakistan, unlocking $1.2B under EFF and RSF, supporting economic recovery, macro stability, and social protection amid global risks.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 03:47:07"}}, "469": {"text": "AG office pays $348m on Clico collapse. The Office of the Attorney General has paid $346.8 m