aud-italian-authorities-seize-art-assets/", "title": "Ursula Andress' $23M Fortune Recovered After Alleged Fraud, Italian Authorities Seize Art & Assets", "description": "Ursula Andress has gotten her financial assets back after allegedly being swindled out of $23 million by her financial advisors. Now, Italian authorities have shared that they recovered her stolen fortune in the form of \u201cworks of art\u201d and other assets. On Thursday (March 26), the law enforcement agency Guardia di Finanza shared the following [...]", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 21:22:58"}}, "579": {"text": "On Thursday (March 26), the law enforcement agency Guardia di Finanza shared the following [...] ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.justjared.com/2026/03/28/ursula-andress-23m-fortune-recovered-after-alleged-fraud-italian-authorities-seize-art-assets/", "title": "Ursula Andress' $23M Fortune Recovered After Alleged Fraud, Italian Authorities Seize Art & Assets", "description": "Ursula Andress has gotten her financial assets back after allegedly being swindled out of $23 million by her financial advisors. Now, Italian authorities have shared that they recovered her stolen fortune in the form of \u201cworks of art\u201d and other assets. On Thursday (March 26), the law enforcement agency Guardia di Finanza shared the following [...]", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 21:22:58"}}, "580": {"text": "Eight players leave England camp ahead of Japan friendly. England boss Thomas Tuchel will have no choice but to ring the changes ahead of Tuesday's friendly with Japan at Wembley Stadium after eight players left the camp on Saturday with a variety of health issues and injury concerns. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.dubaieye1038.com/news/sports/eight-players-leave-england-camp-ahead-of-japan-friendly/", "title": "Eight players leave England camp ahead of Japan friendly", "description": "England boss Thomas Tuchel will have no choice but to ring the changes ahead of Tuesday's friendly with Japan at Wembley Stadium after eight players left the camp on Saturday with a variety of health issues and injury concerns.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 21:22:08"}}, "581": {"text": "Duke And UConn Meet For 6th Time In NCAA Men\u2019s Basketball Tournament. Duke faces UConn in Sunday's NCAA tournament East Region final. Duke holds a six games to four edge in their head-to-head matchups. The teams haven't played since 2014. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://ca.sports.yahoo.com/news/duke-uconn-meet-6th-time-212200592.html", "title": "Duke And UConn Meet For 6th Time In NCAA Men\u2019s Basketball Tournament", "description": "Duke faces UConn in Sunday's NCAA tournament East Region final. Duke holds a six games to four edge in their head-to-head matchups. The teams haven't played since 2014.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 21:22:00"}}, "582": {"text": "AI's arrival complicates Big Tech climate goals, and some worry it's locking in more fossil fuels. Six years ago, Google was confident that by 2030 it would power all operations with electricity generated from clean sources, including wind and solar power, and remove as... ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://japantoday.com/category/tech/ai's-arrival-complicates-big-tech-climate-goals-and-some-worry-it's-locking-in-more-fossil-fuels", "title": "AI's arrival complicates Big Tech climate goals, and some worry it's locking in more fossil fuels", "description": "Six years ago, Google was confident that by 2030 it would power all operations with electricity generated from clean sources, including wind and solar power, and remove as...", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 21:21:33"}}, "583": {"text": "Frosting, sprinkles and layers of fun: Giant cake picnic hits Sydney. Hundreds of bakers head to Sydney's Botanic Gardens to share and savour their colourful creations. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://ca.