 being removed", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 21:34:17"}}, "592": {"text": "Anker\u2019s Smart Display Charger for iPhones Drops to Just $27.99 \u2014 and It\u2019s Unlike Any Charger You\u2019ve Used Before. If you\u2019ve been looking for an excuse to upgrade your iPhone charger, this deal might be the one. The Anker Nano 45W GaN Fast Charging USB-C Charger with Smart Display has dropped to just $27.99 on Amazon \u2014 a solid $12 off its regular price of $39.99. That\u2019s a 30% discount on one of the", "metadata": {"source": "https://cordcuttersnews.com/ankers-smart-display-charger-for-iphones-drops-to-just-27-99-and-its-unlike-any-charger-youve-used-before/", "title": "Anker\u2019s Smart Display Charger for iPhones Drops to Just $27.99 \u2014 and It\u2019s Unlike Any Charger You\u2019ve Used Before", "description": "If you\u2019ve been looking for an excuse to upgrade your iPhone charger, this deal might be the one. The Anker Nano 45W GaN Fast Charging USB-C Charger with Smart Display has dropped to just $27.99 on Amazon \u2014 a solid $12 off its regular price of $39.99. That\u2019s a 30% discount on one of the [...] The post Anker\u2019s Smart Display Charger for iPhones Drops to Just $27.99 \u2014 and It\u2019s Unlike Any Charger You\u2019ve Used Before appeared first on Cord Cutters News .", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 21:34:03"}}, "593": {"text": "of $39.99. That\u2019s a 30% discount on one of the [...] The post Anker\u2019s Smart Display Charger for iPhones Drops to Just $27.99 \u2014 and It\u2019s Unlike Any Charger You\u2019ve Used Before appeared first on Cord Cutters News . ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://cordcuttersnews.com/ankers-smart-display-charger-for-iphones-drops-to-just-27-99-and-its-unlike-any-charger-youve-used-before/", "title": "Anker\u2019s Smart Display Charger for iPhones Drops to Just $27.99 \u2014 and It\u2019s Unlike Any Charger You\u2019ve Used Before", "description": "If you\u2019ve been looking for a