"title": "Pisces \u2653 Weekly Horoscope (30th March - 5th April, 2026): Emotional Growth, Career Focus & Financial Awareness", "description": "Pisces Weekly Horoscope (30th March 2026 to 5th April 2026): This pisces weekly horoscope shows a week of responsibilities and inner transformation. The Moon will be in Leo at the start, then transit into Virgo on 31st March (night), Libra on 3rd April, and Scorpio on 5th April (evening). These transits will activate your Sixth, Seventh, Eighth, and Ninth Houses. You will focus on work, relationships, transformation, and higher learning. Mars will transit into Pisces on 2nd April 2026, increasing energy but also inner restlessness. Discover what Anand Sagar Pathak reveals in this pisces horoscope this week, exploring inspiring weekly astrology predictions for pisces that foster emotional healing, focus, and alignment throughout this weekly horoscope cycle.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 22:00:39"}}, "622": {"text": "Libra on 3rd April, and Scorpio on 5th April (evening). These transits will activate your Sixth, Seventh, Eighth, and Ninth Houses. You will focus on work, relationships, transformation, and higher learning. Mars will transit into Pisces on 2nd April 2026, increasing energy but also inner restlessness. Discover what Anand Sagar Pathak reveals in this pisces horoscope this week, exploring", "metadata": {"source": "https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/astrology/horoscope/pisces-weekly-horoscope-30th-march-5th-april-2026-emotional-growth-career-focus-financial-awareness/articleshow/129875182.cms", "title": "Pisces \u2653 Weekly Horoscope (30th March - 5th April, 2026): Emotional Growth, Career Focus & Financial Awareness", "description": "Pisces Weekly Horoscope (30th March 2026 to 5th April 2026): This pisces weekly horoscope shows a week of responsibilities and inner transformation. The Moon will be in Leo at the start, then transit into Virgo on 31st March (night), Libra on 3rd April, and Scorpio on 5th April (evening). These transits will activate your Sixth, Seventh, Eighth, and Ninth Houses. You will focus on work, relationships, transformation, and higher learning. Mars will transit into Pisces on 2nd April 2026, increasing energy but also inner restlessness. Discover what Anand Sagar Pathak reveals in this pisces horoscope this week, exploring inspiring weekly astrology predictions for pisces that foster emotional healing, focus, and alignment throughout this weekly horoscope cycle.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 22:00:39"}}, "623": {"text": "in this pisces horoscope this week, exploring inspiring weekly astrology predictions for pisces that foster emotional healing, focus, and alignment throughout this weekly horoscope cycle. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/astrology/horoscope/pisces-weekly-horoscope-30th-march-5th-april-2026-emotional-growth-career-focus-financial-awareness/articleshow/129875182.cms", "title": "Pisces \u2653 Weekly Horoscope (30th March - 5th April, 2026): Emotional Growth, Career Focus & Financial Awareness", "description": "Pisces Weekly Horoscope (30th March 2026 to 5th April 2026): This pisces weekly horoscope shows a week of responsibilities and inner transformation. The Moon will be in Leo at the start, then transit into Virgo on 31st March (night), Libra on 3rd April, and Scorpio on 5th April (evening). These transits will activate your Sixth, Seventh, Eighth, and Ninth Houses. You will focus on work, relationships, transformation, and higher learning. Mars will transit into Pisces on 2nd April 2026, increasing energy but also inner restlessness. Discover what Anand Sagar Pathak reveals in this pisces horoscope this week, exploring inspiring weekly astrology predictions for pisces that foster emotional healing, focus, and alignment throughout this weekly horoscope cycle.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-28 22:00:39"}}, "624": {"text": "Badenoch criticised for \u2018peddling dangerous fantasy\u20